data.description: Welcome to your new home. This home has approx. 2,000 sq ft of living space with 3-4 bedrooms. There has been a lot of updating with the roof being newer and furnace, water heater and electric being all updated. There is a 50x60 pole barn with electricity, concrete floor and 14 ft overhead doors. All on 2.84 acres. Located in Charlotte school district. There is also a 31x22 bonus room that has been started but has not been completed.
